      <title>Prabowo 寻求模特助力 1 美元午餐计划实现 8% 增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/prabowo-seeks-models-to-have-1-lunch-program-unlock-8-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[候任总统普拉博沃·苏比安托希望他的免费校餐计划能够释放印尼的增长潜力。两个走上同样道路的亚洲大国为该项目的成功提供了经验教训——同时也起到了警示作用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/prabowo-seeks-models-to-have-1-lunch-program-unlock-8-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
