      <title>亚洲股市有望在日本央行和美联储会议周初上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/asian-stocks-eye-early-gains-into-boj-fed-week-markets-wrap</link>
